Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.86,0:01:05.08,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 如果你能让那美丽的月亮瞬间消失的话 我就给你个吻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.58,0:01:21.43,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事真的可以做到吗? 若你只是在游乐 请快离开 不要来打扰我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:29.44,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,调笑只能让你觉得我在游戏人间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.73,0:01:33.19,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,谁说的贞操 我要赤足逃离
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:37.07,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不能给你任何招待 能和我在这浮世跳一支舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.07,0:01:40.49,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,谁说的冥想 不被幻觉所迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.49,0:01:44.12,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,吟咏和歌 与你交汇的词语 传至今日…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:51.96,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,来自某处的情诗 你的背影不要越走越远
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:59.30,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,喷薄而出的感情 我却当做毫不在乎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:06.68,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,来自某处的情诗 永远不曾离开孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:14.23,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,来自某处的情诗 化作那日泪光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.21,0:22:51.21,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just Singin'Lus, Singin'Las, Set it loose, Every La
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.13,0:22:56.59,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,萍水相逢 You&I Shine
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.59,0:22:58.55,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 Take Flight
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.55,0:23:00.13,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,Shine Twice
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.13,0:23:02.26,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,像在哭泣的Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.39,0:23:03.93,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,偶尔也会心烦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.93,0:23:06.35,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,笑所有的一切都变得如此愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.35,0:23:08.52,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,天真烂漫地描绘着同样的vision
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.52,0:23:10.60,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,不属于任何人的Bright light
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.81,0:23:13.06,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,A Day at a time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.06,0:23:16.53,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,看得见 握得住 带着那里的Style So wild
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.53,0:23:18.70,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,Seasons must change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.70,0:23:20.74,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the flame
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.74,0:23:22.33,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,The song eages the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.33,0:23:25.45,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,不同的法则 不同的作法 翻开新的一页
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.45,0:23:28.33,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,但只有一个景色永不改变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.67,0:23:31.38,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,在这旅途中 迷茫的时候请想起它
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.38,0:23:36.34,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just Singin'Lus, Singin'Las, Set it loose, Every La
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.67,0:23:39.47,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,一边歌唱一边前行 永无止尽
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.47,0:23:44.47,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 Justly Singin'Lus, Singin'Las, Set it loose, Every La
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.81,0:23:47.73,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,闪耀天生的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:52.69,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just Singin'Lus, Singin'Las, Set it loose, Every La
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.02,0:23:55.90,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,兜兜转转 现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.90,0:23:58.28,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,So Just singin'Lus…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.28,0:24:02.20,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,Said a little thing I never ever set to say
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.20,0:24:07.70,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,Tears 被风吹干 Blue
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.20,0:24:11.83,OP-CN,,0000,0000,0000,,Again Singin'My Lu
